{"tid":1063712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊人哋男朋友嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-03-16T03:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T04:07:32.000Z","uid":221616,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17ca45c977c9c1f1053da0a4e7dedec36f1f27f5","tid":1063712,"uid":221616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:50:04.000Z","msg":"［代post］<br />\n試問有邊對情侶拍緊拖嘅時候冇鬧過交？<br />\n之前我同我男朋友鬧交大家冷靜緊嘅 中途都有揾大家嘅朋友傾訴<br />\n聽人哋傾訴嗰個唔係負責聽人哋訴苦嘅咩？<br />\n我真係唔明點解得到嘅係 聽到男朋友講返我係港女<br />\n即係而家港女嘅定義係雙方會鬧交會發脾氣 女方就要做港女？<br />\n咁男方呢？<br />\n我真係唔明點解會比個三唔識七嘅咁樣屌法<br />\n一個男人咁冇風度你都算係數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講嘢咁肉酸<br />\n簡直係侮辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3647bd6d29129ceb29ea0b6e2e16423874be3512","tid":1063712,"uid":45772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:54:27.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"dffe01ebb42ec27b379ff7a9c024915d12691524","tid":1063712,"uid":63418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"咁你d朋友又有冇話返你條仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0e211be35b29dcb60ca2f6d8a92a1b73726832","tid":1063712,"uid":221616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dffe01ebb42ec27b379ff7a9c024915d12691524","tid":1063712,"uid":63418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"咁你d朋友又有冇話返你條仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"唔知佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0f2d5037366e8dfba3997cc177d8fe9131364a","tid":1063712,"uid":89964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"你唔講成件事出黎 點同你討論"},{"pid":"739a479d0480a15f4fafe67b0dd0b629744c3951","tid":1063712,"uid":239510,"like":0,"dislike":0